905
01:07:30,220 --> 01:07:34,230
# Yes, it's the
saddest experience #

906
01:07:34,230 --> 01:07:37,530
# You'll ever know #

907
01:07:37,530 --> 01:07:39,470
# Because one is
the loneliest number #

908
01:07:39,470 --> 01:07:40,470
Roy!

909
01:07:45,540 --> 01:07:47,370
Ta-da!

