940
01:09:38,650 --> 01:09:40,190
# l said yeh, yeh #

941
01:09:40,190 --> 01:09:41,880
- Tôi là Roy O'Baloney vớ vẩn!

942
01:09:41,880 --> 01:09:42,950
- Phải!

943
01:09:42,950 --> 01:09:44,200
- tôi đầy vớ vẩn nè!

944
01:09:44,200 --> 01:09:45,390
chính xác !!

945
01:09:45,390 --> 01:09:48,450
# We'll play a melody
and turn the lights down low #

946
01:09:48,450 --> 01:09:49,690
# So that none can see #

947
01:09:49,690 --> 01:09:55,130
# We gotta do that,
we gotta do that #

948
01:09:55,130 --> 01:09:58,870
# And there'll be no one else
alive in all the world #

949
01:09:58,870 --> 01:10:00,730
# 'Cept you and me #

950
01:10:00,730 --> 01:10:02,610
# Yeh, yeh, yeh, yeh, yeh #

951
01:10:02,610 --> 01:10:04,410
# Yeh, yeh, yeh, yeh #

952
01:10:04,410 --> 01:10:06,950
# My pretty baby,
l never knew such a thrill #

953
01:10:06,950 --> 01:10:09,680
# lt's hard to tell you,
because l'm tremblin' still #

954
01:10:09,680 --> 01:10:12,720
# My pretty baby,
l want you all for my own #

955
01:10:12,720 --> 01:10:14,420
Roy?

956
01:10:20,260 --> 01:10:21,200
Lin!

957
01:10:26,140 --> 01:10:28,740
Đây là ý tưởng của anh ta

958
01:10:29,310 --> 01:10:30,670
- Chon!
- Mặc đồ!

959
01:11:03,210 --> 01:11:04,930
Một buổi tối thật tuyệt để đi dạo

960
01:11:13,720 --> 01:11:14,680
ROY: Lin!

961
01:11:14,680 --> 01:11:16,220
Lin! Lin, kia rồi

962
01:11:16,220 --> 01:11:17,280
Em đang làm gì đó?

963
01:11:17,280 --> 01:11:20,200
tên sát nhân hàng loạt
ở đây !!

964
01:11:20,200 --> 01:11:21,850
Thôi quên đi

965
01:11:29,800 --> 01:11:31,660
- Mấy tên này là ai vậy

966
01:11:31,660 --> 01:11:32,670
Thích khách !!

967
01:11:32,670 --> 01:11:34,170
- Chúng muốn gì ở chúng ta?

968
01:11:34,170 --> 01:11:36,470
- Chúng là người của ta

969
01:11:38,980 --> 01:11:42,310
Ta nghĩ chúng ta cần nói chuyện

970
01:11:51,820 --> 01:11:53,950
Chon Wang --

971
01:11:53,950 --> 01:11:56,790
